							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Best bet is to join a society and buy the recipe books from the wholesaler. They wont be specific to alchemy in anyway but it gives you recipes of all flavors with some alchemy. From there you can use the resources avaliable to you in the society and get artisan levels.
<br />

<br />
P.S. You'll need to get scholar recipe lists in exp zones. The sooner you level and use these, the more recipes at your disposal.<br />_________________<br />27 Troubador of Kithicor
<br />

<br />
<img src=http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v296/Thanatos87/Caius3.bmp></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
