							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If you go Alchemist, I advise you to spend a day Harvesting Roots and Stones of the appropriate tier. (60 each should be enough for Tier 2/scholar). Make as many inks as you can, starting with your secondary ingredients.
<br />

<br />
2 washes/ ink
<br />
1 oil
<br />
1 resin
<br />

<br />
then make your Reagents (it will be "refined trinoid" for sage lvl 10-19)
<br />

<br />
1 reagent/ink
<br />

<br />
then make your Dyes 1/ink
<br />

<br />
then finish off all of your inks.
<br />

<br />
the craft flowChart looks like this:
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">
<br />
# Scholar
<br />
iron gual ink &#40;Scholar 10&#41;
<br />

<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; * iron gual dye &#40;1&#41;&#40;Scholar&#41;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; o Trinoid Reagent &#40;1&#41;&#40;Scholar&#41;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; + Raw Electrum or Turqoise&#40;1&#41;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; + stroma oil &#40;1&#41;&#40;Scholar&#41;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; # raw tuber&#40;1&#41;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; # liquid&#40;1&#41;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; # paraffin wax candle&#40;1&#41;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; + paraffin wax candle&#40;1&#41;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; o stroma wash &#40;1&#41;&#40;Scholar&#41;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; + raw tuber&#40;1&#41;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; + liquid&#40;1&#41;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; + paraffin wax candle&#40;1&#41;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; o paraffin wax candle&#40;1&#41;
<br />
